   Harvard Univ Hebaria, Cambridge, MA 02138 USA.
   Univ Wisconsin, Dept Bot, Madison, WI 53706 USA.
   Royal Bot Gardens, Jodrell Lab, Mol Systemat Sect, Richmond TW9 3DS, Surrey, England.
